        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We walked as strangers unaware of Him,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But in His glory God shined deep within,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Infusing His own element in us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This precious essence was our Lord Jesus."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What glory! How attractive was this light!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How we appreciated such a sight!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our first reaction was belief in Him—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "This precious God has placed Himself within."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our first reflection of this element"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Reflected Jesus back to God, Who sent"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His own response to count as righteousness"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our faith in Him Who was infused in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But we would hold to this reality,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our Jesus Christ in us our all to be,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Enjoying all He is abundantly,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Content to have this One eternally."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thus God could never be so satisfied;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Knowing that we cared only to abide"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In our experiences of His Son,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not caring for His goal to make us one."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Still He would seek those faithful saints who’d hear"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His call to give up everything so dear,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To offer up their individual Christ;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To come together for the Body life."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
